{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_04_03",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜 3話 桜の花びらのおまじない",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Few days after",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 2.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "……にこっ\nうーん、違うわね。もっと自然に……にこっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Nico.\nHmm‚ that's not it. More naturally… Nico.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（リハーサルで怜の動きがぎこちなかったから）\n（心配になって楽屋まで様子を見に来たが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Rei's movements were awkward during rehearsal.)\n(I got worried and came to the dressing room to check…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "こうかしら……にこっ\nいえ、やっぱりこう……にこ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like this… Nico.\nNo‚ maybe like this… Nico~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……怜、何をしているんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Rei‚ what are you doing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "きゃっ！　{user}さん！？\nいつからそこに！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kyaa! {user}-san!?\nSince when were you there!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "というか、女子の楽屋にこっそり侵入して\n無言で近づくなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I mean‚ secretly sneaking into the girls' dressing room\nand approaching me silently…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "何度も声を掛けたのに気付かなかったんじゃないか\nそんなに集中して、鏡の前で何をしていたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Didn't you notice even though I called you several times?\nWhat were you so focused on in front of the mirror?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "こ、これは……別にこの間言われたことを気にして\n笑顔の練習をしていた訳じゃありませんから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-this… It's not like I was practicing smiles\nbecause of what you said earlier!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "気にしていたのか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were bothered by it‚ huh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "ち、ちがっ……！　私はせめて\n『怖い』と思われないように笑顔でいようかと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-that's not it…! I was just trying to smile so that\nI wouldn't be thought of as \"scary\"…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それで鏡の前で笑顔の練習を？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And so you were practicing smiles in front of the mirror?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "……はい\nでも、どうしても自然に笑えなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes.\nBut no matter how hard I try‚ I can't smile naturally…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "笑顔を意識すればするほど、普段の自分が\nどんな風に笑っていたのか分からなくなるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The more I focus on smiling‚\nthe more I lose sight of how I usually smile…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "こんなことにこだわるなんておかしいですよね\n誰も私の笑顔なんて求めていないのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's ridiculous for me to be so fixated on this.\nNobody is asking for my smile…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことはない。千紗と雫も言ってたんだろ？\nいつも厳しい怜がたまに見せる優しい笑顔が素敵だって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not true. Chisa and Shizuku said the same thing‚ right?\nThey said they love the gentle smile that strict Rei shows occasionally.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "……確かに、二人とも\n私の笑顔が好きだって言ってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Indeed‚ both of them…\nThey said they like my smile.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私はいつもどんな風に笑っていたんでしょう\n笑おうとすると……ほら、頬が引きつってませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But how did I usually smile…?\nLook‚ my cheeks… They're twitching‚ aren't they?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.7457204521,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……確かにちょっと引きつってるな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah‚ they're slightly twitching.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "はあ……、やっぱり……\nやればやるほど顔が引きつってくるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*Sigh*… As I thought…\nThe more I try‚ the more my face twitches.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたら私は自然に笑えるんでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How can I naturally smile?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに難しいことじゃないんだが……\nよし、怜、今から少し付き合ってくれないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not that difficult…\nAlright‚ Rei‚ can you accompany me for a bit from now on?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.7,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5333.333333300005,
          "startTime": 139.0333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cherryblossom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "cherryblossom-00-night",
      "startTime": 138.8
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cherryblossom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "cherryblossom-00-night",
      "startTime": 138.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "綺麗……ライブ会場の近くにこんな場所があったなんて\n知りませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Beautiful…There was such a place near the live venue.\nI didn't know",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ここは地元では有名な桜の名所なんだ。ライトアップ\nされた夜桜は昼間とはまた違う美しさがあるだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a famous cherry blossom spot in the local area.\nThe illuminated cherry blossoms have a different beauty at night‚ don't they?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cherryblossom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "cherryblossom-00-night",
      "startTime": 156.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_03-rei015.m4a",
